data.name: radLabel24.Text
data.value: Please note that when you have signed this form and paid the initial payment of your fees, you are formally and regularly enrolled. As a student, you are to respect, observe, abide by, and uphold the school's rules and regulations and its academic policies. If later on you will decide to withdraw, THERE WILL NO REFUND MADE EVEN IF YOU HAVE NOT ATTENDED A SINGLE DAY OF CLASSES.
